  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要设计一个教育内容审核流程。用户举报不良内容后，系统要先经过验证码确认，然后自动分类判断是否需要人工复核。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Person",
        "REPORT",
        "CAPTCHA",
        "AUTO_CLASSIFIER"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。那如果验证码不通过，这条举报是直接丢弃吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CAPTCHA",
        "TRASH"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，直接进垃圾箱，标记为无效举报。验证码通过后，自动分类器判断内容是否真的违规。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CAPTCHA",
        "AUTO_CLASSIFIER"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "那自动分类器如果判断不是违规内容，是不是也要通知用户审核未通过？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AUTO_CLASSIFIER",
        "NOTIFY_NO"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，走NOTIFY_NO分支，通知举报者，同时这条记录也进垃圾箱。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NOTIFY_NO",
        "TRASH"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把NOTIFY_NO指向TRASH。那如果自动分类器判断是违规内容呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AUTO_CLASSIFIER",
        "C_CROWD"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "进入众包复核环节C_CROWD，由教育LMS门户的审核员二次确认。这里有个分叉：复核通过就正式通知举报者YES，不通过就回到NO分支。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C_CROWD",
        "NOTIFY_YES",
        "NOTIFY_NO"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "C_CROWD的NO分支指向NOTIFY_NO我理解，但NOTIFY_YES之后呢？是不是就结束了？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NOTIFY_YES"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "不是，NOTIFY_YES还要做两件事：一是触发ADD_EVENT记录到学生数据库，二是走CLASSIFIER_TRAINER更新模型。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NOTIFY_YES",
        "ADD_EVENT",
        "CLASSIFIER_TRAINER"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "收到。那NOTIFY_NO这边除了进垃圾箱，是不是也需要训练反馈？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NOTIFY_NO",
        "CLASSIFIER_TRAINER"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，NOTIFY_NO也要走CLASSIFIER_TRAINER，但这里有个细节——NOTIFY_NO的trainer是连到LMS门户，而NOTIFY_YES的trainer是连到学生数据库。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NOTIFY_NO",
        "NOTIFY_YES",
        "CLASSIFIER_TRAINER"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，我刚才把两个CLASSIFIER_TRAINER画成同一个节点了，需要拆成两个吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CLASSIFIER_TRAINER"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "逻辑上是同一个训练服务，但数据源不同。你可以画一个CLASSIFIER_TRAINER，从NOTIFY_NO和NOTIFY_YES分别连入，标注清楚目标系统就行。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CLASSIFIER_TRAINER",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白了，我调整一下连线。还有，CLASSIFIER_TRAINER需要回传更新给AUTO_CLASSIFIER对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CLASSIFIER_TRAINER",
        "AUTO_CLASSIFIER"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，标注Update关系，形成闭环优化。ADD_EVENT是独立的学生数据库写入，不需要回传。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CLASSIFIER_TRAINER",
