      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下节点归属：REPORT和NOTIFY_NO属于ContentCDN，CAPTCHA和AUTO_CLASSIFIER属于GradeSync，C_CROWD属于LMS门户，TRASH和NOTIFY_YES属于ClassroomService，ADD_EVENT和NOTIFY_YES的trainer属于StudentDB？",
      "elements_involved": [
